/m²K)<br>\n-- Maximum weight/sash: 400 Kg<br>\n -- Maximum acoustic insulation: Rw = 43 dB\n</p>','https://www.cortizo.com/en/sistemas/ver/74/4600-lift--slide-hi.html'),(11,'Cor 4200','Cortizo','Sliding Systems ','sliding','4200 (1).png','4200 (2).jpg','4200 (3).jpg','<p>Description:  A versatile sliding system with a thermal bridge.<br>\n-- Transmittance: Uw from 1,5 (W/m²K)<br>\n-- Maximum weight/sash: 200 Kg<br>\n -- Maximum acoustic insulation: Rw = 39 dB\n</p>','https://www.cortizo.com/en/sistemas/ver/13/4200-sliding.html'),(12,'Cor 6500-6500 Plus ','Cortizo','Sliding Systems ','sliding','6500 (1).jpg','6500 (2).jpg','6500 (3).jpg','<p>Description:  Non-thermal sliding window system with more glazing capacity and reduced central sash encounter of only 40 mm of section.<br>\n-- Transmittance: Uw from 2,2 (W/m²K)<br>\n-- Maximum weight/sash: 240 Kg<br>\n -- Maximum acoustic insulation: Rw = 36 dB\n</p>','https://www.cortizo.com/en/sistemas/ver/21/6500-plus-sliding--6500-sliding.html'),(13,'Cor 80 Industrial','Cortizo','Hinged Systems','hinged','Cor 80 Industrial (1).png','Cor 80 Industrial (2).jpg','Cor 80 Industrial (3).jpg','<p>Description:  Hinged system that responds to the most severe climatic requirements thanks to its thermal break with 45 mm tubular polyamide strips.<br>\n-- Transmittance: Uw ≥ 0.8 (W/m2K)<br>\n-- Maximum weight/sash: 160 Kg<br>\n -- Maximum acoustic insulation: Rw up to 46 dB\n</p>','https://www.cortizo.com/en/sistemas/ver/153/cor-80-industrial-tb.html'),(14,'Alu-Steel','Cortizo','Hinged Systems','hinged','Alu-Steel (1).png','Alu-Steel (2).png','Alu-Steel (3).png','<p>Description:  Inspired by classic line designs, this new system allows to combine aluminium outstanding performance values with a steel-alike appearance.<br>\n-- Transmittance: Uw ≥ 0,83 (W/m2K)<br>\n-- Maximum weight/sash: 160 Kg\n</p>','https://www.cortizo.com/en/sistemas/ver/160/alu-steel-tb.html'),(15,'Cor 70 Hidden Sash (Invisible Arch) ','Cortizo','Hinged Systems','hi